  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007161_4_1392-1457",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1392-1457",
      "markText": "但是个人无意识有赖于更深的一个层次；这个层次既非源自个人经验，也非个人后天习得，而是与生俱来的。我把这个更深的层次称为集体无意识。",
      "totalCount": 624,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1392&rangeEnd=1457",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55e32370813ab694cg011e63?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1392&rangeEnd=1457"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007161_4_6333-6420",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6333-6420",
      "markText": "事实上，我们必须指出，通过传统的演变和传承，形象在变得越漂亮、越崇高、越全面的同时，越是远离个人经验。虽然我们能够摸索着进入形象，感知到它的某些面向，但是原初的经验已然丧失。",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6333&rangeEnd=6420",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55e32370813ab694cg011e63?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6333&rangeEnd=6420"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007161_4_4267-4318",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4267-4318",
      "markText": "从本质上讲，原型是一种经由成为意识以及被感知而被改变的无意识内容，从显形于其间的个人意识中获取其特质。",
      "totalCount": 340,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4267&rangeEnd=4318",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55e32370813ab694cg011e63?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4267&rangeEnd=4318"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007161_4_12510-12567",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "12510-12567",
      "markText": "人们开始思考其形象时，他们是在所谓的“理性”的帮助之下完成的——实际上，理性只不过是一切人类偏见及短视的总和而已。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=12510&rangeEnd=12567",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55e32370813ab694cg011e63?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=12510&rangeEnd=12567"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007161_4_3894-3993",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3894-3993",
      "markText": "原始部落文化所关涉的原型已然经过了某种特殊方式的改造。它们不再是无意识的内容，而是已然被改造成了根据传统、以秘传教学形式传授的意识法则。这一具有代表性的表达手段，表示原本源自无意识的集体意识的转移。",
      "totalCount": 285,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3894&rangeEnd=3993",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55e32370813ab694cg011e63?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3894&rangeEnd=3993"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007161_4_1534-1577",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1534-1577",
      "markText": "它在所有人身上别无二致，并因此构成具有超个人性的共同心理基础，普遍存在于我们大家身上。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1534&rangeEnd=1577",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55e32370813ab694cg011e63?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1534&rangeEnd=1577"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007161_4_4755-4796",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4755-4796",
      "markText": "他们的无意识心理有一种无法抗拒的欲求——把一切外在的感官体验同化为内在的心理事件。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4755&rangeEnd=4796",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55e32370813ab694cg011e63?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4755&rangeEnd=4796"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007161_4_6651-6710",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6651-6710",
      "markText": "很自然，我们越熟悉它们，我们就会越持续地使用它们，把它们打磨得光滑流畅，结果只剩下了陈腐的表面性及毫无意义的自相矛盾。",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6651&rangeEnd=6710",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55e32370813ab694cg011e63?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6651&rangeEnd=6710"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007161_4_21362-21456",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "21362-21456",
      "markText": "在意识领域我们是自己的主人；我们似乎是“主因”自身。但是如果我们跨过阴影之门，我们会恐怖地发现我们是未曾见过的主因的客体。这一认识必定令人不悦，因为没有什么会比发现自己无能为力更具幻灭性。",
      "totalCount": 208,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=21362&rangeEnd=21456",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55e32370813ab694cg011e63?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=21362&rangeEnd=21456"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007161_4_3772-3790",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3772-3790",
      "markText": "在处理远古时代以降业已存在的普世形象",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3772&rangeEnd=3790",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55e32370813ab694cg011e63?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3772&rangeEnd=3790"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007161_4_14274-14349",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "14274-14349",
      "markText": "承认精神贫乏是危险的，因为穷人欲望缠身；谁有欲望，谁就会遭灾。有一句瑞士谚语把它说得很透彻：“每个富人背后站着一个魔鬼，而每个穷人背后站着两个魔鬼。”",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14274&rangeEnd=14349",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55e32370813ab694cg011e63?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=14274&rangeEnd=14349"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007161_4_1662-1761",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1662-1761",
      "markText": "个人无意识的内容主要为人们所谓的带感情色彩的情结（feeling-toned complexes）；它们构成心理生活的个人及私人面向。另一方面，集体无意识的内容众所周知是原型（archetype）。",
      "totalCount": 168,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1662&rangeEnd=1761",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55e32370813ab694cg011e63?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1662&rangeEnd=1761"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007161_4_1606-1628",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1606-1628",
      "markText": "唯有借能够意识的内容在场，心理的存在方可辨识",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1606&rangeEnd=1628",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55e32370813ab694cg011e63?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1606&rangeEnd=1628"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007161_4_5051-5109",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5051-5109",
      "markText": "相反，它们是心理的内在的、无意识的冲突事件的象征表达，心理经由投射变得与人的意识相连——换言之，反映在自然事件之中。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5051&rangeEnd=5109",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55e32370813ab694cg011e63?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5051&rangeEnd=5109"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007161_4_21656-21748",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "21656-21748",
      "markText": "任何外部历史条件都不过是威胁着我们生命的真正危险的诱因或者起点。它们是导致错觉的当下政治——社会制度。我们不应随意把它们视为外部条件的必然结果，而应该把它们视为由集体无意识促成的结果。",
      "totalCount": 130,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=21656&rangeEnd=21748",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55e32370813ab694cg011e63?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=21656&rangeEnd=21748"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007161_4_26551-26601",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "26551-26601",
      "markText": "如果没有了传统的道德，精神生活与肉体生活便会厚颜地相处得更加和谐，而且常常因此保持着更为健康的状态。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300007161&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=26551&rangeEnd=26601",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/55e32370813ab694cg011e63?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=26551&rangeEnd=26601"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300007161_5_814-892",
      "chapterUid": 5,
